--- Hall OT vortex problem with MLAU two-dimensional code (serial version) ------
 To activate the Hall term, set HALL being 1 and tune iner_p in global.hpp
 Default initial condition is the same as adopted in Amano, T. (2015) J. Comput. Phys. 299, 863

